14
00:00:41,553 --> 00:00:44,034
work related that are mainly covering

15
00:00:44,034 --> 00:00:48,621
long-term commuting and frequent absences from the main home

16
00:00:48,621 --> 00:00:52,037
from traveling for business or weekly roundtrips

17
00:00:52,037 --> 00:00:54,447
between the main house and a pied-a-terre close

18
00:00:54,447 --> 00:00:56,247
from workplace.

19
00:00:56,247 --> 00:00:58,203
