74
00:03:25,263 --> 00:03:26,863
avoiding interactions.

75
00:03:26,863 --> 00:03:30,065
They also facilitate access to transport networks,

76
00:03:30,065 --> 00:03:33,506
schedules, locations, the ticketing, etc.

77
00:03:34,586 --> 00:03:39,342
For mobility, various skills can be very useful.

78
00:03:39,342 --> 00:03:42,633
Mastering foreign languages ​​especially English,

79
00:03:42,633 --> 00:03:45,302
is thus part of the ongoing development

80
00:03:45,302 --> 00:03:47,076
of an European labor market.

81
00:03:47,754 --> 00:03:50,819
English is also helpful since the person is brought

82
00:03:50,819 --> 00:03:53,510
to make business trips abroad.

83
00:03:54,031 --> 00:03:56,826
In addition, we considered the ability of people

84
00:03:56,826 --> 00:03:59,115
to read a map and orientate oneself in space

85
00:03:59,115 --> 00:04:02,491
but also skills such as the ability to consider

86
00:04:02,491 --> 00:04:06,006
the opportunities of moving to a new region.

87
00:04:06,559 --> 00:04:08,827
The way people are able

88
00:04:08,827 --> 00:04:12,298
to appropriate transportation time to value,

