143
00:07:09,767 --> 00:07:11,700
compared to the rest of the population,

144
00:07:11,700 --> 00:07:14,389
but they do not want to move or use

145
00:07:14,389 --> 00:07:16,124
forms of mobility.

146
00:07:16,124 --> 00:07:20,760
